Package
Description
shopify
The root package for the Shopify application.
shopify.Controllers
This package contain Rest controllers that house the various endpoints of the application
shopify.Data.DTOs
This package contains Data Transfer Objects (DTOs) used for data exchange between layers.
shopify.Data.Models
This package contains entity classes that define the data models used in the application.
shopify.Repositories
This package contains repository interfaces for performing database operations.
shopify.Security
This package contains security related configurations
shopify.Services
This package contains the various services that define the business logic of the application
shopify.Utility
This package contains POJO classes that are used to generate and manage RSA keys.
